title.rendered: French Bistro Bar Stool – Special Offer Model

content.rendered:
This item is due to be discontinued. Price available whilst stocks last. For the standard French Bistro Bar Stool, please click HERE.

The French Bistro Bar Stool is made from welded steel and powder coated in two colours.

The French Bistro Bar Stool is stackable and is only suitable for indoor use. This is a commercial grade stool.

We also offer other French Bistro items to complete your venue.

Held in stock for delivery in 2-4 days.
